<br />Yep that about summed it up XD
<br />
<br />not only that but he did other questionable things... like write to Spr-RAM with $2004.  While that would work... It's completely impractical for all your sprite data.
<br />
<br />Plus he did some stuff that would downright just <em>not work</em>.  Including declaring vars in zero page with ".db $80" and then expecting the area in RAM to be $80 when the ROM is run (when it wouldn't be)

		

